	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You smile at a creature, say something friendly, and make a welcoming or beckoning gesture, magically influencing their mind to see you as a friendly face.</em></p><p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target is &amp;Reference[Charmed] by you. The target views you as a friendly aquaintance, and cannot harm you, but is not compelled to do as you say.</p><p>If you or one of your allies do anything harmful to the target, the spell ends. When the spell ends, the creature knows it was charmed by you.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional creature for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
